data.description: Open House Sunday (12/3) 1-3 p.m is now canceled.  We have an accepted offer, sorry for any inconvenience.  Located on a quiet street just blocks away from Snider high school, you'll find this three bed, two full bath ranch home.  New storm door, front door, garage door, HVAC and roof.  All you need to do is make it your own.  Two separate living spaces and a three seasons room (heated by a gas fireplace) allows the chance to spread out.  The primary bedroom has its own full bathroom for added privacy.  The fenced in back yard is perfect for pets to run around.  This is your chance to live in a great community.  Contact me or your agent today for a tour.
